description:
In this karaoke-themed worship video, we'll be singing the popular hymn "Take the World but Give Me Jesus." This song is perfect for worship or small group settings, and is sure to bring a smile to your face!

If you're looking for a fun and easy karaoke song, try "Take the World but Give Me Jesus." This classic hymn is sure to brighten up any worship service or gathering! Whether you're singing along or just listening, this song is sure to bring joy!

First Line: Take the world, but give me Jesus, All its joys are but a name
Title: Give Me Jesus
Author: Fanny Crosby
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel.
